      "writtenOn": "2026-07-13T18:30:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The intent here was to differentiate between the various types of SPI flash.  Intel spi flash is laid out differently than AMD, is laid out differently than an FPGA.  The intent is that we could differentiate and add things like validity checks in the future.\n\nI suspect you want to change this to \u003cHostSOCManufacturer\u003eSpiFlash",
      "revId": "7ededf61f85edc96ebb92629c6e4b031ba5d8eea",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
